  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/56fbb0d66ed7d4602e0adf2f92ed7d41.poster.avif?t=1745894069\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/56fbb0d66ed7d4602e0adf2f92ed7d41.webm?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/56fbb0d66ed7d4602e0adf2f92ed7d41.mp4?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Welcome Aquascapers and Fish Lovers!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deskquarium is an Aquascape simulation game that is suitable for you fish and aquascape lovers, where you can enjoy the beauty of aquascape while doing your activities on the computer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game will have various types of aquariums, fish, trunk, plants, rocks, gravel, filtrations, and also co2 diffusers so that your aquascape feels more immersive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Aquarium</strong>, there's a  multiples aquariums you can have in this game.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/1da870a990a47c0589e831ee4197e167.poster.avif?t=1745894069\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/1da870a990a47c0589e831ee4197e167.webm?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/1da870a990a47c0589e831ee4197e167.mp4?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fish</strong>, there's a lot of fish types with multiples color and shapes you can have in this game.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/ba959880a981c610b7b3fb4e5b9fdc11.poster.avif?t=1745894069\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/ba959880a981c610b7b3fb4e5b9fdc11.webm?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/ba959880a981c610b7b3fb4e5b9fdc11.mp4?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Plant</strong>, there's a lot of Plant types with multiples color and shapes you can have in this game.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >with wavy effects for the plants, and growing mechanism, it will give more immersive experience for your aquascaping experiences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/fb6733bc8ba6af52a14eab1bfafba76b.poster.avif?t=1745894069\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/fb6733bc8ba6af52a14eab1bfafba76b.webm?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/fb6733bc8ba6af52a14eab1bfafba76b.mp4?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Trunk</strong>, there's a multiple trunk with their own unique shapes you can have in this game.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/13aeeee86b3e8de0b7241816cd943db6.poster.avif?t=1745894069\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/13aeeee86b3e8de0b7241816cd943db6.webm?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/13aeeee86b3e8de0b7241816cd943db6.mp4?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rocks</strong>, there's multiple rocks with their type, sand, black rock, and etc.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/7ab08e440c8ce8bd6d14404e65b8ffbd.poster.avif?t=1745894069\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/7ab08e440c8ce8bd6d14404e65b8ffbd.webm?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/7ab08e440c8ce8bd6d14404e65b8ffbd.mp4?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Filtrations</strong>, there's multiple types of water pump for aquarium filtrations.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/a3a94c4ac8a2c4a0f82ed69a3a2b211d.poster.avif?t=1745894069\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/a3a94c4ac8a2c4a0f82ed69a3a2b211d.webm?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/a3a94c4ac8a2c4a0f82ed69a3a2b211d.mp4?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CO2 Diffuser</strong>, there's multiple types of water pump for aquarium filtrations.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/0d757bcbbee88b6de9b225213511a870.poster.avif?t=1745894069\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/0d757bcbbee88b6de9b225213511a870.webm?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278680/extras/0d757bcbbee88b6de9b225213511a870.mp4?t=1745894069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By carrying the Idler theme, you can stay focused on your work, and allow you to decorate your aquascape occasionally.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So what are you waiting for fish and aquascape lovers? <strong>Wishlist Now</strong> Fish Pals!<br>or maybe you can try the demo for Free!</p>",
